Package: rnotify
Type: Package
Title: RStudio Addin: Script Runner with Notifications
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Nicholas Birdsong [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Nicholas Birdsong <github@nicholasbirdsong.com>
Description: Provides a simple RStudio addin that runs the currently active script, 
    plays a sound notification, and sends a macOS Reminder when finished.
    Useful for keeping track of script completion, especially for long-running code.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    rstudioapi,
    beepr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3

